fm: string longestPalindrome(string s) {     int len = s.size();     int P[len][len];     memset(P, 0, len * len * sizeof(int));     int maxL = 0, start = 0, end = 0;     for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++)     {       for (int j = 0; j < i; j++)       {         P[j][i] = (s[j] == s[i] && (i - j < 2 || P[j + 1][i - 1]));         if (P[j][i] && maxL < (i - j + 1))         {           maxL = i - j + 1;           start = j;           end = i;         }       }       P[i][i] = 1;     }     return s.substr(start, end - start + 1);   }

fm: int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {     int count[256];     memset(count, -1, 256 * sizeof(int));     int len = 0, maxL = 0;     for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++, len++)     {       if (count[s[i]] >= 0)       {         maxL = max(len, maxL);         len = 0;         i = count[s[i]] + 1;         memset(count, -1, 256 * sizeof(int));       }       count[s[i]] = i;     }     return max(len, maxL);   }
